Name: Here to There
About the game: Here to There is a singleplayer puzzle FPS. The player moves through different areas, solving (sometimes) deceptive problems in each of a much larger labyrinth of spaces. Content Includes Problem solving. Mysterious environments. Unexpected mechanics. Pacing and difficulty variations.
